Looking at the universe of stocks we cover at Dividend Channel, on 12/10/14, Bank of the James Financial Group Inc will trade ex-dividend, for its quarterly dividend of $0.05, payable on 12/26/14. As a percentage of BOTJ's recent stock price of $9.99, this dividend works out to approximately 0.50%.



